{
  "stem": "22869.6",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I didn't know that he charges.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He thought I was in a Russian soldier.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He'll probably takes you for free.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So a few of the guys that I knew from my hometown too were also there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he comes to Michalovce, and everybody goes down and gives him a few Czech crowns.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I have no money.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I have nothing on me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I spoke a little Russian too, which by now I forgot.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I try to explain, look, I come from concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I says, everything today is supplied by us, food and transportation for free.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That's what the UNRRA has decreed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I says, why would you want to charge me?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I have no money.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He pulls out his revolver, and he says he's going to shoot me if I don't pay him.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So some of the other people who were on the truck too put together a few crowns that they gave him, and they're, like, released me.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That was my one more chance to lose my life in that-- in that-- after the three years.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this is how I walked from the place where he dropped me off.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I came to the house that we once owned.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I walk in in the yard, and I find the daughter of my uncle who was taken with me to Majdanek.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She's there.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We recognize each other.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We started crying and hugging and kissing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I ask her where is her mother.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She says her mother left with-- with-- with one of the-- and her brother someplace, but she'll be soon back.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So here I am in the-- in the-- in the house where I-- where we used to live.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
